title: Tender for the Supply of X-Ray Developer for Automatic Processing, X-Ray Fixer for Automatic Processing, Film X-Ray Dental Standard Size 3x4cm, Film X-Ray Dental Occlusal Size 5x7cm, X-Ray Film, Blue Base Automatic Processing Size - 24x30 cm, 35.6x35.6cm, 18x24cm, 35.6x43.2cm, 30x40cm
decision_details: the proposal made by Hon. Maithripala Sirisena, Minister of Health, to proceed with the procurement of the above items as recommended by the Standing Cabinet Appointed Procurement Committee (SCAPC), was approved by the Cabinet.
